---
title: Carb Smart Middle Eastern-Style Double Beef Bowls with Creamy Hummus Dressing
description: Skip the pita and instead layer this bowl with all your favourite shawarma toppings: roasted carrots, sweet tomatoes, pickled onions, olives and a creamy hummus dressing!

